OL,6,FLast month, it was reported that a
OL,7,Fmeeting between Sir Keir and
OL,8,Fcampaigners had been cancelled, with
OL,9,Fclaims officials were attempting to
OL,10,Fhave the contents of a bill watered
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,FIt is understood concerns relate to
OL,14,Fwho the duty of candour would apply to.
OL,16,FIn an update last week, Commons leader
OL,17,FLucy Powell said the Government will
OL,18,Ftake "whatever time is necessary" to
OL,19,Fdevelop a law which "meets the
OL,20,Fexpectations" of the Hillsborough
OL,21,Ffamilies.
