OL,6,FInquest director Deborah Coles said a
OL,7,Fdelay in a Bill being introduced to
OL,8,FParliament by the anniversary would be
OL,9,F"disappointing" but that it is
OL,10,Fimportant the proposed legislation
OL,11,Ffully meets campaigners' hopes.
OL,13,FNinety-seven football fans died as a
OL,14,Fresult of a crush at the FA Cup semi-
OL,15,Ffinal between Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,16,FForest at Hillsborough Stadium in
OL,17,FSheffield.
OL,19,FThey were unlawfully killed amid a
OL,20,Fnumber of police errors, an inquest
OL,21,Fjury ruled in 2016.
