OL,6,F"Establishing a duty of candour could
OL,7,Fprevent this, help us learn from
OL,8,Ffailures and ensure bereaved and
OL,9,Fsurvivors are properly supported. This
OL,10,Fis why a Hillsborough Law is so
OL,11,Furgent."
OL,13,FLobby Akinnola from CBFFJ, whose
OL,14,Ffather died in the pandemic, said:
OL,15,F"Those bereaved by Covid have seen
